[2] LANGUAGE:- "Python"

PROBLEM STATEMENT:- Check whether number is palindrome or not.

CODE NO :- 2

n=int(input("enter number"))
temp=n
rev=0

while n>0:
    r=n%10
    rev=rev*10+r
    n=n//10

if temp==rev:
    print("palindrome")
else:
    print("not palindrome")

